<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA522_08_IH_0005_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema522_08.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema522_08_ih_0005">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="5" class="is_star fraction_box_title">
          <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
              <span lang="y">서하는 자전거를 타고 한 시간에</span>
              <div class="mixed_fraction">
                <span>21</span>
                <div class="fraction_box"><span>3</span><span>4</span></div>
              </div>
              <span lang="y">&nbsp;㎞ 를 갔습니다. 서하가 같은 빠르기로 자전거를 탈 때, 1시간 20분 동안 갈 수 있는 거리는</span>
            </div>
            <div class="fraction_txt">
              <span lang="y">몇 ㎞인지 식을 쓰고 답을 구해보세요.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box align_center justify_center dir_col">
          <div class="input_area">
            <div class="input_row flex align_center gap_10">
              <span class="label_gray">식</span>
              <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap fraction1 hint_up">
                <math-field data-answer-single="21(3)/(4)×1(1)/(3)" text-align="center" placeholder="&nbsp;"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>=</span>
              <!-- <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap fraction2 hint_up">
								<math-field
									data-answer-single="29"
									text-align="center"
									placeholder="&nbsp;"
								></math-field>
							</div> -->
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="29"></math-field>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input_row flex align_center gap_10">
              <span class="label_gray">답</span>
              <!-- <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap fraction3">
								<math-field
									data-answer-single="29"
									text-align="center"
									placeholder="&nbsp;"
								></math-field>
							</div> -->
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="29"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>㎞</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <div class="flex align_center gap_10">
                  <span>1시간 20분=1</span>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span class="mark_error up">20<i>1</i></span
                    ><span class="mark_error">60<i>3</i></span>
                  </div>
                  <span>시간=1</span>
                  <div class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>3</span></div>
                  <span>시간입니다.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex align_center gap_10 mt_36">
                  <span>(서하가 1시간 20분 동안 갈 수 있는 거리)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex align_center gap_10 mt_36">
                  <span>=21</span>
                  <div class="fraction_box"><span>3</span><span>4</span></div>
                  <span>×</span>
                  <span>1</span>
                  <div class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>3</span></div>
                  <span>=</span>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span class="mark_error up">87<i>29</i></span
                    ><span class="mark_error">4<i>1</i></span>
                  </div>
                  <span>×</span>
                  <div class="fraction_box">
                    <span class="mark_error up">4<i>1</i></span
                    ><span class="mark_error">3<i>1</i></span>
                  </div>
                  <span>=</span>
                  <span>29(㎞)</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key" lang="y">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
